::DarkMouse::
In her quarters she slammed her fists into the wall.  Again and again she 
hit the wall as hard as she could.  It sent out a vibrating noise through 
out the room and into the hallway.  She stopped for a moment and thought 
things through.
"Get a grip mouse.  He's a high ranking commander.  Give up the ideas.  I'm 
nothing more that a bot to command.  Get used to it. Besides, he's got a bot 
to himself and would never think of me as such anyway."

She sighed and sat o the edge of her bed.

"OK, let's get the logic circuits in order.  He has another bot.  I have had 
no contact with him until now.  He's my commander.  And I need to get a 
grip.  Ok got find Megatron and gets some orders and find something to do.  
That will help."

She walked out of her quarters with her logic circuits straightned out and 
whistled down the hallway out to find Megatron and gets something to do. She 
was dettermend not to get involved with any bot as long as she lived.
